Quest:About the Astrals

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search

Quest Information


Prequest:
Door to the Stars

Given By: Llewella Corey

Giver Location: Celestia Base Camp
This is a side quest.

Goals:
Visit Celestial Trainers
Hand In: Completes Automatically

Reward:

30
200


Leads to:

None

Quest Dialogue


This page is for recording a complete Quest Dialogue of all the conversation and story during a quest.
This includes NPC discussions, Narrator statements, and Creature speeches.


Documentation on how to edit this page can be found at Template:QuestInfobox/doc.

Hints, guides, and discussions of the Wiki content related to About the Astrals should be placed in the Wiki Page Discussion Forums.

Search for content related to About the Astrals in the Central Wiki Forums by clicking here.
